2011


Overview
Chirpify is a social media loyalty platform that offers social engagement and loyalty solutions for marketers. It enables brands to convert mobile and social actions into rewards and brand loyalty by activating consumers for "in-stream" marketing and commerce, participation and conversion. The platform allows brands to generate a currency exchange between social media and loyalty programs to enhance …


